Package: tp-docker
Version: 1.0.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: docker-ce, docker-ce-cli, containerd.io, docker-buildx-plugin, docker-compose-plugin, acl
Maintainer: Technical Platform <noreply@example.com>
Description: Docker CE complete installation for Technical Platform WSL
 This metapackage installs the complete Docker CE suite including:
 - Docker CE Engine
 - Docker CLI
 - containerd runtime
 - Docker Buildx plugin
 - Docker Compose plugin
 The installation automatically configures user group membership and POSIX ACLs
 on the Docker socket for immediate sudo-less execution.
